com.kstechnologies.nirscannanolibrary

Class KSTNanoSDK.NanoGattCharacteristic

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kstechnologies.nirscannanolibrary.KSTNanoSDK.NanoGattCharacteristic
  • Enclosing class:
    KSTNanoSDK

    public static class KSTNanoSDK.NanoGattCharacteristic
extends java.lang.Object
    Collection of BluetoothGattCharacteristics that need to be set upon enumeration. ALL members need to be set otherwise an error will be reported when trying to read/write the characteristic indicating it is null. NOTE: Some characteristics have both write and notify properties, but are in the GATT table as two separate instances. It is important that the properties of the characteristics be used to assign the proper GATT characteristic to each NanoGattCharacteristic
